article.headline: Montana 43, Sacramento St. 7
article.story: MISSOULA, Mont. -- Cole Bergquist threw four touchdown passes and ran for another score to help Montana rout Sacramento State 43-7 on Saturday. Bergquist completed 17 of 19 passes for 290 yards for the Grizzlies (6-1, 2-1 Big Sky). Marc Mariani had eight receptions for 131 yards and two touchdowns, and Mike Ferriter caught five passes for 119 yards and two touchdowns. The Grizzlies held the Hornets (3-4, 1-3) to 250 yards.
